# Step by Step 
## 1. Install tools
* install Ubuntu
* Install NS-2
* Install nam
* Install Python (Matplotlib and OS library)

```commandline


sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade -y
sudo apt install build-essential autoconf automake libxmu-dev -y
wget http://www.isi.edu/nsnam/dist/ns-allinone-2.35.tar.gz
./install
ns

```
